- 'Most active users' refers to users with the highest number of total views; 
- 'Membership details' include membership name, monthly price, and yearly price; 
- 'Total views' is the total number of views a user has made; 
- 'Total downloads' is the total number of downloads a user has made.

External knowledge: 
- 'top 10 most voracious readers' refers to the top 10 users who have accessed the most content resources; 
- 'devoured the most content' refers to accessing the most content resources; 
- 'in the past month' refers to within the last 30 days.
